429
00:33:21,048 --> 00:33:23,168
Thế nếu cô thua thì sao?

430
00:33:23,808 --> 00:33:24,208
Ta...

431
00:33:24,408 --> 00:33:25,808
Ta cũng không làm khó cô.

432
00:33:26,369 --> 00:33:27,649
Nếu cô thua

433
00:33:28,048 --> 00:33:29,328
